o uart uses the quickdev combo cabel and runs at 115200
o compile works under os x
o seriall screen works under os x
o os x see masstorage device


POC SREG
o makefile include 'programm' for avrdude with dragon_isp
o uart uses the quickdev combo cabel and runs at 115200
o compile works under os x
o seriall screen works under os x
o to debug the sreg or the fsm reduce the speed of the avr
    o program fuse divide clock by 8 internally
    o set uart baud speed to 9600 by setting UBRR1=25
    o change speed in screen session

